   * Answer Key: Include a fully detailed explanations section at the very end of the output document, detailing why correct choices are mathematically/scientifically valid.`;
            }

            prompt += `\n\nEnsure that all outputs are in robust Markdown format, avoiding complex HTML wrappers, so that they can easily be copied directly into typical text processors or learning management systems.`;

